Edition:
Quote: If some genius or other among the umemployed would invent a means for destroying the "spugs" wholesale, he would make a good thing out of our sparrow nuisance, for we have them here in millions, and they have devoured just about as much of our oats as would have supplied porridge to half the unemployed in the colony until prosperity returns again.
